  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was late in the day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And because-- because it was getting dark and the Germans were still offering resistance and the war wasn't over yet-- this was the 6th of May-- we decided to go back to our headquarters and to come back the following morning.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was another reason for that, because when I got back and I had a chance to exchange some information with the military government officer, I found out that the mayor of the town had told them that in that town, there had been-- there were a group of Polish and Hungarian Jewish young women who had been on a death march for a long time and whose SS guards had locked them into a vacant factory building.",
      "word_count": 79
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when the guard saw the handwriting on the wall, they still wanted to destroy them and put dynamite charges on the factory building, which fortunately didn't go off because of the rains.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then the guards put on civilian clothes and disappeared.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we knew we had to do-- and that they were in deplorable condition.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we knew we had to do something, had to come back with [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] great medical reinforcements the following morning.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's precisely what we did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was now May 7th, and we went back with the medics.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the factory building was pointed out to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I approached it by jeep and got out, saw these walking skeletons scurrying back and forth to-- to a water pump that was in the center of the yard in front of the factory.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And and they-- I mean, they-- I had never seen anything as bad as that.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
